conbody.p:
The following function receives the result of the evaluation of two other functions as
      parameters (for instance, this is useful if you have image references and you want to see
      thumbnail images stored in the same
      folder):image[href]{
 content:oxy_url(oxy_base-uri(), oxy_replace(attr(href), 
    '.jpeg', 'Thumbnail.jpeg'));
}

The following function uses an editor variable as the first parameter to point to the 
      installation
      location:image[href] {
    content: oxy_url('${oxygenHome}', 'logo.png');
}
